# Going Deeper

#### It's important to make the distinction between equality, equity, and justice when tackling topics of education. Take a look at the following image, created by Tony Ruth (@lunchbreath on Twitter/X):
<br>

<a href="https://docs.google.com/presentation/d/1EnQ8lf1l2FVqU0AVvwODPcwW9ERlD8vle2ELAyqKIjA/edit?usp=sharing" target="blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><img src="https://images.code.org/1deaadb47c55ad112dd414bdf93b93f1-image-1732573038355.17.14 PM.png" alt="Four panels show a Giving Tree analogy for inequality, equality, equity, and justice."></a>
